#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:3 10c47fab77ab435d8c0b340bb02ac39b
msgid "2. Layouting"
msgstr "2. 排列圖層"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:5 b5dc35f768224703a8a312a25b86730c
msgid ""
"Now that we have Aka's head loaded in to our project and we can save and "
"load it, the next step is to lay out the model for rigging, this step is "
"called Layouting."
msgstr ""
"現在我們的專案中已經載入了 Aka 的頭部，下一步我們要將圖層們分類、排列整齊以便捏製模型 (Rigging)。"
"這個動作叫做\\ **排列圖層 (Layouting)**\\。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:6 8c4819247aa047a0a90f32a887755de6
msgid "You can think of layouting as building out the skeleton for our model."
msgstr "你可以將它想成建立模型的骨架。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:8 75a0277b20554a37ae331e708db0db27
msgid "For this chapter we'll be following the diagram below"
msgstr "在這個單元中，我們會跟著以下的圖示分類。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:12 7ed4acaf72b54c77ad249a45274e4d4b
msgid ""
"We'll be using the basic :doc:`Node </creator/nodes/node>` to build out "
"this skeleton, which will make some rigging easier later."
msgstr ""
"我們會使用\\ :doc:`節點 (Node) </creator/nodes/node>`\\來建立骨架，這會讓我們等等捏造模型更容易。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:15 48930548dc3a48fb9e898857b774222a
msgid "Creating our skeleton"
msgstr "建立骨架"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:18 b61c3714b39d49fda0ed64dd82d3376a
msgid "1. Adding a Node"
msgstr "1. 建立一個節點"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:25 6ac7c49af1cf4ac1b0b7675cc5e89334
msgid ""
"To add new nodes to the tree right click an existing node and select the "
"type of Node you want within the ``Add`` submenu, in this case we want "
"the ``Node`` node type."
msgstr ""
"要在模型中建立節點，右鍵點選已經存在的節點，並在\\ ``新增``\\內選擇你所需要的節點類型。"
"在這裡我們選擇\\ ``節點``\\。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst d66f562196ca4170b44c12f87c952950
msgid ""
"The ``Add`` submenu will add the Node as a child to the node you right "
"clicked!"
msgstr ""
"``新增`` 子選單會將新增的節點變成你所選的節點的子節點。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst afce31fbed1c4cb69d7dfb3c5f918012
msgid ""
"See the :doc:`Nodes </creator/nodes/index>` page for more information "
"about how parenting works!"
msgstr ""
"想知道更多關於子節點的敘述，請見\\ :doc:`節點 </creator/nodes/index>`\\。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:43 43c287240b1f44d08758e7202efe56fd
msgid "2. Renaming a Node"
msgstr "2. 幫節點命名"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:50 df03e3a4d1ab4401988e6b6af1dc5ba5
msgid ""
"After adding our new Node, we'll see it appear as \"Unnamed Node\" within"
" the node tree. We should probably rename it so that it's easier to to "
"know what it does at a glance."
msgstr ""
"當我們新增完節點之後，你會看到它在模型中的名字為\\ "未命名 節點"\\。"
"我們應該重新命名它，以便我們在之後製作時知道它代表什麼。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:52 b3491299ce8d48738ca74accd2b152f6
msgid ""
"Click the node and within the Inspector panel, rename the node to \"Neck "
"Root\""
msgstr ""
"點擊節點，在下方的檢視器中重新命名節點為\\ "Neck Root"\\。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:58 3f31dd0f6ac4482ba2e5bd747f8d0aa8
msgid "3. Transforming a Node"
msgstr "3. 變形（Transforming）節點"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst d57ab04f8a3644d289638c2d4f005bbf
msgid ""
"If you look in the viewport with our ``Neck Root`` selected you will see "
"the following gizmo pop up."
msgstr ""
"當你點選了\\ ``Neck Root``\\節點時，你會看到在右側的視窗中出現了一些東西。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst 86dedb48be354b9ebea109e3961668bb
msgid ""
"This gizmo tells you where the node is in the scene, the colors represent"
" where the X, Y and Z axis of the node are pointing"
msgstr ""
"這些東西告訴你該節點的位置，而線條代表著 X 軸、Y 軸及 Z 軸所代表的方向。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst 2c4b6474efcf4aef9b958b1d3536454c
msgid ""
"X is red, Y is green, Z is blue. Z is currently obscured by the fact that"
" it's pointing away from the camera."
msgstr ""
"X 是紅色，Y 是綠色，而 Z 是藍色。目前 Z 因為指向鏡頭的反方向，所以它被隱藏起來了。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:79 10151ee27bdf45f59b57dcb29c69aa18
msgid ""
"Either by dragging the move gizmo (the button that looks like arrows "
"pointing in 4 directions) or by editing the Translation section in the "
"Inspector, move Neck Root to the bottom of the neck."
msgstr ""
"按住移動標誌（長得像箭頭指向四個方向）或者改變檢視器中 \"移動\"的數字，將節點移動到脖子的底部。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:88 54fcce0846944021af0a219f1e66412e
msgid "4. Finishing the basic Layout"
msgstr "4. 完成基本圖層排列"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst c5422c09cbc74f9a9cd72a62bb2df590
msgid ""
"With these 3 basic functions you should be able to create a skeleton, "
"remember that ``Add`` adds nodes as children of another node and that the"
" position of every node is *relative* to their parent node!"
msgstr ""
"有了這三個基礎操作，你就可以建立角色骨架了！"
"記得\\ ``新增``\\會將節點新增為另一節點的子節點，而每一個節點都是相對於其父節點的！"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst 47c0030bea9e4c058945cb24f8fd8ded
msgid "Try to re-create this layout using the techniques above."
msgstr "使用我們剛剛教你的方法試著複製這個骨架。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:101
#: 0288f3945b6a43d28a069f582c6c369b
msgid "A challenge"
msgstr "小挑戰"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst ab03b0379e474095a28bbf8bcbad73eb
msgid ""
"Now that you know the basics of creating a layout, try creating "
"additional layout points for the nose and back hair!"
msgstr ""
"現在你知道怎麼製作最基本的骨架了，試試看幫角色的鼻子及後面的頭髮也加上骨架！"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst:118
#: 61ed33b7ea3b4241922c868175c3acdd
msgid "Moving things around"
msgstr "移動節點之間的相對關係"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst f137e6b7c68b4b45b9c0d9dd2a901839
msgid ""
"Now that we have our skeleton, it's mostly just about moving things in to"
" the right place, drag and drop all the Part Nodes (the ones with the "
"color palette icon) in to their place!"
msgstr ""
"現在我們已有了骨架，接下來，請將所有部件節點（圖示為調色盤的那些）拖放到正確的位置。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst 7d6b7528410d41e4a4e196be4bbf6e8d
msgid "Try to roughly follow this layout!"
msgstr "試試看大概照著這樣排！"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst 650d691de05044d4bbe7e94b2a62ac71
msgid ""
"You can now try to select Neck Root and rotate the node around the Z axis"
" (3rd box in the Rotation section or using the rotate Gizmo), notice that"
" all the children of the Neck Root rotate with it!"
msgstr ""
"現在你可以選擇 Neck Root 節點並試著旋轉它（檢視器中 \"旋轉\"欄位或者節點旁邊的旋轉控制軸）"
"你可以發現所有子節點都會跟著一起轉動！"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst 76b5bb5490704d80bf31ac6b4ff910b8
msgid "Congratulations! You've finished layouting your model, for now at least."
msgstr "恭喜你！你已經完成你目前的排列圖層。"

#: ../../creator/first-model/tutorial02.rst 4272f4c261644bc2a31e0b4fca356771
msgid ""
"You can download the resulting model file :download:`here <tutorial-"
"aka02.inx>`, if you need a reference!"
msgstr ""
"你可以下載\\ :download:`完成檔 <tutorial-aka02.inx>` \\作為比對！"

